{"tid":2103694,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"他知道哭是沒用的","createTime":"2020-07-11T11:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T15:58:44.000Z","uid":11081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"381a0a8a3cf7b671a455540a82bf23e5197f99db","tid":2103694,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:32:15.000Z","msg":"利物浦前軍醫尷尬爆料：我縫過謝拉特「細佬」<br />\n<br />\n馬斯近日向傳媒透露，在2014年利物浦對般尼茅夫的一場足總盃上，謝拉特在一次爭球中受傷，私處撕裂出血：「比賽完結後，謝拉特走過來對我說：『醫生，你要看看這裡』，我低頭看，到處都是鮮血，心想這一定非常痛。我試圖回憶自己接受過的醫學培訓，但在培訓中根本不會教你縫合一條陰莖。我當時在想，我不希望自己縫合的第一條陰莖是謝拉特的，但最終就是這樣。」<br />\n<br />\n在謝拉特數年前的自傳當中，亦有提及過這段「慘痛」的經歷，提到馬斯醫生當時非常不安：「我脫下球褲和內褲後，看過最後一眼，心想不會是跟老朋友告別吧......馬斯醫生當時很不自在，他一定寧願留在家中照顧學童，不過我沒說太多，希望他全神貫注。最後他也做得很好，我沒有感到痛楚，四針就完成。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://football.fanpiece.com/m/cornerflagnews/c1380035.html?page=football\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fm%2Fcornerflagnews%2Fc1380035.html%3Fpage%3Dfootball&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=d579bf61\" target=\"_blank\">https://football.fanpiece.com/m/cornerflagnews/c1380035.html?page=football</a>"},{"pid":"ae639a7d3885cd5f7ac91ce1015b4fbaff957e2c","tid":2103694,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"為左利物浦<br />\n子孩根都差d保唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135bbe46043d8d60c10ea133430f92fc60cee009","tid":2103694,"uid":61999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:04:14.000Z","msg":"我來縫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc79731062610734ccce8d80b643a5595075a47","tid":2103694,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae639a7d3885cd5f7ac91ce1015b4fbaff957e2c","tid":2103694,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"為左利物浦<br />\n子孩根都差d保唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202